<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Помощь в управлении самокатом</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #87cefa;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #87cefa;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background-color: #87cefa;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
